    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <h3>Is ChatGPT better than Gemini for writing?</h3>
    <p>Yes. ChatGPT consistently produces more natural, engaging prose. Gemini is competent but more factual and less creative in tone.</p>
    <h3>Which is better for coding?</h3>
    <p>ChatGPT for quick scripts and explanations; Gemini for large codebase analysis (2M context) and Google Colab integration.</p>
    <h3>Can I use both together?</h3>
    <p>Absolutely. Many professionals use ChatGPT for writing and creative tasks, and Gemini for research and Google Workspace automation.</p>
    <h3>Which has the better free tier?</h3>
    <p>Gemini's free tier is more generous in 2026, offering Gemini 2.5 Flash with fewer daily limits than ChatGPT's free GPT-4o access.</p>
